nes over and over and people are getting bored with them. Post under here ideas for places you would like to adventure. ToV will be posted as a raid in approximately 2 weeks, as said in my post under RESIST GEAR, no one will be going if their resists are not up to standards. More info about this will be posted soon. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub64.ezboard.com/uralronaalvina.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ralrona Alvina</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFF00>(4/13/02 11:46:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub64.ezboard.com/fchaoticnightsfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Raids</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><center> SOL Possibilities </center><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
1. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Akheva Ruins</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> - Seems only to be used to kill the boss mobs.<br>
2. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Maiden's Eye</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> - the lil fort in the center of the zone.. the vampires<br>
3. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Fungus Grove</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> - Can do the Caller Quest ( <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=1570">Summoning Biesties</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> yes thats how the &quot;walkthrough&quot; spells it )<br>
4. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Tenebrous Mountains</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> - that dang Vampire Castle<br>
5. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> The Deep</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> - never been. but i know THO is there ^_^<br>
6. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Umbral Plains</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> - i wanna kill one of those damn Assassin buggers instead of running<br>
7. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Acrylia Caverns</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> -  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> might</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> be &quot;camped&quot; 24/7 i know lots of mages go there, as i have been asked, for AE groups. but there's the <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=1569">Ring of Fire</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> Quest. We could try the first 3 or 4 &quot;waves&quot; of the quest and just reset it instead of doing the 5th crazy boss guy<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><center> ROK Possibilites</center><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
1. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Chardok</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> - been to this zone a total of 4 times, 5 times max. 2 before upgrade. <br>
2. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Howling Stones</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> - Have to get everyone key's before you <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> plan</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> going here.          <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=682">Key to Howling Stones/Charasis</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
3. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Sebilis</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> - its one of my favorite zones. The frogs are <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> so</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> laughable now.          again, people need keys <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=86">Key to Sebilis</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
Above all, I think 9/10 zones are easily accessible. the only ones that <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> might</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> pose problems and/or someone would need <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> help</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> entering, would be Acrylia. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=148181>Ral's Gear</a>

