Velks Lab - I would love to hit that zone with the guild, I also need the spider silk that drops off the spiders.  The graphic looks like a pearl necklace.  Some other casters might need them also for the shawl quest<br>
Howling Stones - I've never been there and I don't have the key.  We could do a key raid for people that don't have the keys one day.  Then when everyone gets key, we go obliterate HS.<br>
CoM - That was ok exp and loot, we could do reavers again.<br>
Chardok - I've only been there like 2 times, but once you get to royals, it's good exp.  Plus good loot.<br>
SG - That place seems to be good exp and ok loot.  Quest gems and caster armor.  We need to figure out how to safely pull or kill that stuff in the water hole near that one place we always camp at.  I don't know how many times ya'll been here, but I've been there only twice and I like it there.<br>
SolB - I think we can take giants, they're good exp if Naggy is not raided.  We could kill Efreeti to get some boots if no one has.  (sorry if it sounds like I'm only going after caster stuff, but these are the only places I've been to.  I don't get around much because of my work schedule =)<br>
Naggy and Vox - Perhaps we could get a raid for these dragons in the future.  Get our alts to 52 and kill these SoB's!  I've been to many of these dragon raids and all have been failures.  I want to see these dragons go down at least once!<br>
The Grey - Some of us still need EB item and this place would make it easy to get one.  Plus this place has very good exp and loot.  Also, the snake temple is in the middle of the zone.  I've never been in there to kill but I've heard of very nice loot to drop in there.<br>
Amber mentioned Tenebrous Mountains Vampire Castle - I would like to hit there, I heard of very good loot in there.  But those vampires are very nasty.  They make themselves invisible so if you go to pull one that's not invisible, you may end up with alot of them.  Good exp there also<br>
Scarlet Desert - The sunmen at the top of one of the mountains are pretty good exp up to level 60!  I know that also one of the named sunmen drop an item for the +20 something wisdom shield quest.  But that place is usually camped =\ <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub64.ezboard.com/uciado.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ciado</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFF00>(6/30/02 10:41:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub64.ezboard.com/fchaoticnightsfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Raids</span><hr size=1> HoT in ToV can be done with the same folks you've been using for Umbral.<br>
